190
00:13:33,221 --> 00:13:36,204
- Tomorrow you'll settle it with the doctor.
- Unhooded?

191
00:13:37,939 --> 00:13:42,854
# The long, long, long, long shits...

192
00:13:43,099 --> 00:13:48,351
# ...run and melt. They need a bedpan...

