00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:05,253
[...that we slept all
night like pumpkins.]

197
00:14:05,365 --> 00:14:08,242
[And so, the day after we
woke up fresh and rested...]

198
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:09,742
[...ready to start again.]

199
00:14:10,389 --> 00:14:15,235
- Well, at this point...
> All: # The long, long, long, long shits...

200
00:14:15,413 --> 00:14:21,717
# ...run and melt. They need a bedpan...

201
00:14:21,896 --> 00:14:23,517
# ...from the sister. #

202
00:14:32,248 --> 00:14:33,290
I warn you:

203
00:14:33,504 --> 00:14:36,081
