buffoonery, or I'll separate you.

204
00:14:36,220 --> 00:14:38,527
I'll send you all to
different floors and wards.

205
00:14:40,225 --> 00:14:41,982
- Who wanted the bedpan?
- He did!

206
00:14:48,779 --> 00:14:49,725
(SASSAROLI LAUGHS)

207
00:14:52,648 --> 00:14:54,405
Sassaroli: There's
nothing to laugh about!

208
00:14:54,481 --> 00:14:56,885
630 of cholesterol, 3,2 of glycaemia.

209
00:14:58,588 --> 00:14:59,910
First of all no more cigars!

210
00:15:02,424 --> 00:15:06,459
A litre and three quarters, with
a three percent of B6 solution.

211
00:15:08,602 --> 00:15:10,532
- Who saw the Madonna?
- He did!

212
00:15:19,769 --> 00:15:23,466
Bipolar electroencephalogram.

213
00:15:24,351 --> 00:15:26,484
And who asked for the chaplain?

214
00:15:27,610 --> 00:15:29,569
Well! Call Don Ulrico.

215
00:15:36,299 --> 00:15:41,184
- And you, what's wrong with you?
- Professor, you won't believe it.

216
00:15:41,323 --> 00:15:43,524
Antani like a traction
for two, even if it were...

217
00:15:43,699 --> 00:15:46,412
...a tarred supercazzola, it
is unhooked towards right.

218
00:15:46,652 --> 00:15:47,491
